normal imports, and uvicorn error handling\n- **factory/server.py**: Fixed product name in response message (Silverpond → Silverforge)\n- **tests/test_server.py**: New comprehensive test suite for server functionality\n- **pyproject.toml**: No changes needed (dependencies correctly declared as hard dependencies)",
